                  , his former wife, Sarah, being then living
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>GEORGE DRIVER sworn. I am the father of Mary Driver: The prisoner drew my daughter in, I never knew any thing of it till two days after; I never saw him till afterwards.</p>
               <p>GEORGE LIMMING sworn. - I am clerk of St. Leonard, Shoreditch; these are true copies from the register-book, I have examined them, (reads):"John Aird, of this parish, Batchelor, and 
